OL,4,CIran bans cryptocurrency mining for
OL,5,Cfour months after blackouts
OL,6, Iran has announced a four-month ban on
OL,7, the energy-consuming mining of
OL,8, cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin after
OL,9, cities suffered unplanned blackouts.
OL,11,FPresident Hassan Rouhani told a cabinet
OL,12,Fmeeting the main cause of the blackouts
OL,13,Fwas a drought that had affected
OL,14,Fhydro-electric power generation.
OL,16,FBut he said cryptocurrency mining, 85%
OL,17,Fof which is unlicensed, was draining
OL,18,Fmore than 2GW from the grid each day.
OL,20,FAn estimated 4.5% of all Bitcoin mining
OL,21,Ftakes place in Iran.
